Title: WD-40 smart straw multi purpose penetrant spray 450ml
Description: A classic multi-purpose product, WD-40 Multi-Use Smart Straw spray does it all, from stopping that hinge's irritating squeak to loosening jammed components and lubricating gears, chains and mechanisms. Smart Straw technology makes reaching hard to get into spots simpler than ever, directing the WD-40 liquid straight into tight spaces for targeted lubrication exactly where it's required. If wider coverage is needed Spray2Ways technology means all you need do is flip the Smart Straw down to rest against the can and press to dispense WD-40 via the can's standard nozzle.
